input:

import math
n1= int(input("Enter First number:"))
n2=int(input("Enter Second number:"))
n3= int(input("Enter third number:"))
GCD1 = math.gcd(n1,n2)
GCD2=math.gcd(GCD1,n3)
LCM = n1*n2/GCD2
print("LCM is ",LCM)
print("GCD is ",GCD2)

output:

Enter First number:10
Enter Second number:5
Enter third number:15
LCM is  30.0
GCD is  5
